1409
01:18:57.215 --> 01:18:58.630
[grunts]

1410
01:19:01.046 --> 01:19:02.289
[cackles]

1411
01:19:05.741 --> 01:19:07.328
[fuses sizzling]

1412
01:19:07.466 --> 01:19:09.020
