1413
01:19:10.090 --> 01:19:12.161
- [Princess Peach grunts]
- [Mario exclaims]

1414
01:19:12.299 --> 01:19:14.301
♪ ♪

1415
01:19:14.439 --> 01:19:15.647
MARIO:
Woo-hoo!

1416
01:19:20.445 --> 01:19:22.965
