1418
01:19:35.598 --> 01:19:37.289
[both grunt]

1419
01:19:43.468 --> 01:19:45.711
[whooshing]

1420
01:19:45.850 --> 01:19:47.783
[Mario grunts]

1421
01:19:47.921 --> 01:19:50.026
