1425
01:19:56.550 --> 01:19:58.517
It didn’t have to be this way.

1426
01:19:58.655 --> 01:20:01.555
I know there’s still
some good in there.

1427
01:20:01.693 --> 01:20:03.937
- [Bowser roars]
- [Princess Peach gasps]

1428
01:20:05.835 --> 01:20:08.217
♪ ♪

1429
