Mario!

1452
01:22:02.434 --> 01:22:03.642
Go.

1453
01:22:03.780 --> 01:22:04.989
Save her.

1454
01:22:13.411 --> 01:22:15.137
[both growling]

1455
01:22:15.275 --> 01:22:17.484
